      "content": "but there isn't anyone to care, that's the point. my coworkers just see a name on a slack channel, and my family is halfway across the country. if i just... drifted away, it would be so seamless. no mess, no drama, just a quiet exit. do you think people actually notice when someone just fades into the background?",
